      "id": "DS0006",
      "data_source": "Web Credential",
      "data_component": "Web Credential Usage",
      "detects": "Monitor the use of application access tokens to interact with resources or services that do not fit the organization baseline. For example, an application that is not meant to read emails accessing users’ mail boxes and potentially exfiltrating sensitive data, or a token associated with a cloud service account being used to make API calls from an IP address outside of the cloud environment.",
